    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>简单记录一下vue-cli构建项目，真的简单记录。</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 全局安装 vue-cli</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install --global vue-cli</span><br><span class="line"># 创建一个基于 webpack 模板的新项目</span><br><span class="line">$ vue init webpack my-project</span><br><span class="line"># 安装依赖，走你</span><br><span class="line">$ cd my-project</span><br><span class="line">$ npm run dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="初始化选项如下-最后按回车use-NPM就可以啦"><a href="#初始化选项如下-最后按回车use-NPM就可以啦" class="headerlink" title="初始化选项如下,最后按回车use NPM就可以啦"></a>初始化选项如下,最后按回车use NPM就可以啦</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue init webpack vue-project</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  A newer version of vue-cli is available.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  latest:    <span class="number">2.9</span><span class="number">.3</span></span><br><span class="line">  installed: <span class="number">2.9</span><span class="number">.1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">? <span class="function">Project <span class="title">name</span> <span class="params">(vue-project)</span>  <span class="comment">// 项目名称</span></span></span><br><span class="line">? Project name vue-project</span><br><span class="line">? <span class="function">Project <span class="title">description</span> <span class="params">(A Vue.js project)</span>  <span class="comment">// 项目描述</span></span></span><br><span class="line">? Project description A Vue.js project</span><br><span class="line">? Author (GL &lt;<span class="number">873928073</span>@qq.com&gt;)  <span class="comment">// 作者</span></span><br><span class="line">? Author GL &lt;<span class="number">873928073</span>@qq.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line">? <span class="function">Vue <span class="title">build</span> <span class="params">(Use arrow keys)</span>  <span class="comment">// 是否安装编译器</span></span></span><br><span class="line">? Vue build standalone</span><br><span class="line">? Install vue-router? (Y/n) <span class="comment">// 是否安装 vue-router（路由）</span></span><br><span class="line">? Install vue-router? Yes</span><br><span class="line">? Use ESLint to lint your code? (Y/n) <span class="comment">// 是否需要使用 ESLint 来检查你的代码</span></span><br><span class="line">? Use ESLint to lint your code? Yes</span><br><span class="line">? <span class="function">Pick an ESLint <span class="title">preset</span> <span class="params">(Use arrow keys)</span></span></span><br><span class="line">? Pick an ESLint preset Standard</span><br><span class="line">? <span class="function">Set up unit <span class="title">tests</span> <span class="params">(Y/n)</span> n <span class="comment">// 是否需要安装测试功能。</span></span></span><br><span class="line">? Set up unit tests No</span><br><span class="line">? Setup e2e tests with Nightwatch? (Y/n) n</span><br><span class="line">? Setup e2e tests with Nightwatch? No</span><br><span class="line">? Should we run `npm install` <span class="keyword">for</span> you after the project has been created? (reco</span><br><span class="line">mmended) (Use arrow keys)</span><br><span class="line">&gt; Yes, use NPM</span><br><span class="line">  Yes, use Yarn</span><br><span class="line">  No, I will handle that myself</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/7f17893a71ff4c65a2eeb1b02d8e9e39/xmlnote/WEBRESOURCE525db9b82a81be11842301ac0a8bf683/576" alt="vue-cli"></p><h3 id="初始完后执行-npm-run-dev-命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。"><a href="#初始完后执行-npm-run-dev-命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。" class="headerlink" title="初始完后执行 npm run dev 命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。"></a>初始完后执行 npm run dev 命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。</h3><p>vue.png</p><h3 id="初始文件解析"><a href="#初始文件解析" class="headerlink" title="初始文件解析"></a>初始文件解析</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── build                           <span class="comment">// 编译配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── build.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── check-versions.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── utils.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── vue-loader.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── webpack.base.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── webpack.dev.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   └── webpack.prod.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">├── config                          <span class="comment">// 项目基本设置文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── dev.env.js                  <span class="comment">// 开发配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── index.js                    <span class="comment">// 配置主文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── prod.env.js                 <span class="comment">// 编译配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules                    <span class="comment">// 项目依赖包文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">├── src                             <span class="comment">// 我们的项目的源码编写文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── assets                      <span class="comment">// 初始项目资源目录</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── logo.png</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── components                  <span class="comment">// 组件目录</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── HelloWorld.vue          <span class="comment">// 测试组件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── router                      <span class="comment">// 路由配置文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── index.js                <span class="comment">// 路由配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── App.vue                     <span class="comment">// APP入口文件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── main.js                     <span class="comment">// 主配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── <span class="keyword">static</span>                          <span class="comment">// 资源放置目录</span></span><br><span class="line">├── .babelrc</span><br><span class="line">├── .editorconfig</span><br><span class="line">├── .eslintignore</span><br><span class="line">├── .eslintrc.js                    <span class="comment">// ESLint配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── .gitignore</span><br><span class="line">├── .postcssrc.js</span><br><span class="line">├── index.html                      <span class="comment">// 项目入口文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── package.json                    <span class="comment">// 项目依赖包配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── package-lock.json               <span class="comment">// npm5 新增文件，优化性能</span></span><br><span class="line">└── README.md                       <span class="comment">// 项目说明文档</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="" alt="directory.png"></p><h2 id="根据自己需求修改点跟加点东东"><a href="#根据自己需求修改点跟加点东东" class="headerlink" title="根据自己需求修改点跟加点东东"></a>根据自己需求修改点跟加点东东</h2><h3 id="重配src目录"><a href="#重配src目录" class="headerlink" title="重配src目录"></a>重配src目录</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── api                             <span class="comment">// 接口调用工具文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    <span class="comment">// 接口调用工具</span></span><br><span class="line">├── components                      <span class="comment">// 组件文件夹，目前为空</span></span><br><span class="line">├── config                          <span class="comment">// 项目配置文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    <span class="comment">// 项目配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── css                             <span class="comment">// css 样式存放目录</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── common</span><br><span class="line">│   │   ├── base                    </span><br><span class="line">│   │   │   ├── _base.scss          <span class="comment">// 基础样式</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   │   ├── _reset.scss         <span class="comment">// reset</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   │   ├── _mixin.scss         <span class="comment">// mixin &amp; function</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   │   └── _variables.scss     <span class="comment">// 全局变量</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── components              <span class="comment">// 全局公共组件</span></span><br><span class="line">│   │       ├── _footer.scss</span><br><span class="line">│   │       └── _header.scss</span><br><span class="line">│   └── common.scss                 <span class="comment">// 主样式文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── img                             <span class="comment">// 图片</span></span><br><span class="line">├── page                            <span class="comment">// 我们的页面组件文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">├── router                          <span class="comment">// 路由配置文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    <span class="comment">// 路由配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── store                           <span class="comment">// vuex</span></span><br><span class="line">│   ├── modules                     <span class="comment">// vuex项目模块文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    <span class="comment">// vuex主文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── utils                           <span class="comment">// 常用工具文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    <span class="comment">// 常用工具文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── App.vue                         <span class="comment">// APP入口文件</span></span><br><span class="line">└── main.js                         <span class="comment">// 主配置文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置-static"><a href="#配置-static" class="headerlink" title="配置 static"></a>配置 static</h3><p>文件如果是放在 src 目录里面，则每次打包的时候，都需要打包的。这回增加我们的打包项目的时间长度。而且，一些地方放的文件，我们一般是不会去修改的，也没必要 npm 安装，直接引用就好了。可以根据自己的情况，对这些可以不进行打包而直接引用的文件提炼出来，放在资源目录里面直接调用，这样会大大的提高我们的项目的打包效率。<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── css             <span class="comment">// 放一些第三方的样式文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── font            <span class="comment">// 放字体图标文件</span></span><br><span class="line">├── image           <span class="comment">// 放图片文件，如果是复杂项目，可以在这里面再分门别类</span></span><br><span class="line">└── js              <span class="comment">// 放一些第三方的JS文件，如 jquery</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="路由懒加载"><a href="#路由懒加载" class="headerlink" title="路由懒加载"></a>路由懒加载</h3><p>详见 <a href="https://router.vuejs.org/zh-cn/advanced/lazy-loading.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">路由懒加载</a></p><h3 id="组件全局注册"><a href="#组件全局注册" class="headerlink" title="组件全局注册"></a>组件全局注册</h3><p>详见 <a href="https://lguoliang.github.io/Blogs/2018/05/17/vue%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C/">组件全局注册</a></p><h3 id="ESLint规则修改，在-eslintrc-js中的rules添加"><a href="#ESLint规则修改，在-eslintrc-js中的rules添加" class="headerlink" title="ESLint规则修改，在.eslintrc.js中的rules添加"></a>ESLint规则修改，在.eslintrc.js中的rules添加</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 结尾分号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'semi'</span>: [<span class="string">'off'</span>, <span class="string">'always'</span>],</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 缩进</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'indent'</span>: <span class="string">'off'</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'vue/script-indent'</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">'error'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'baseIndent'</span>: <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="请求使用axios"><a href="#请求使用axios" class="headerlink" title="请求使用axios"></a>请求使用axios</h3><h4 id="Installing"><a href="#Installing" class="headerlink" title="Installing"></a>Installing</h4><p>Using npm:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install axios</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>Using cdn:<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h4 id="跨域处理，接口本地代理"><a href="#跨域处理，接口本地代理" class="headerlink" title="跨域处理，接口本地代理"></a>跨域处理，接口本地代理</h4><p>配置config里的index文件，找到proxyTable，配置如下<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">proxyTable: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">'/v2/**'</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    target: <span class="string">'https://api.douban.com'</span>, <span class="comment">// 你接口的域名</span></span><br><span class="line">    secure: <span class="literal">false</span>, <span class="comment">// 如果是https接口，需要配置这个参数</span></span><br><span class="line">    changeOrigin: <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment">// 如果接口跨域，需要进行这个参数配置</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="可以本地模拟数据，虽然实际不怎么用得上，还是记录一下吧"><a href="#可以本地模拟数据，虽然实际不怎么用得上，还是记录一下吧" class="headerlink" title="可以本地模拟数据，虽然实际不怎么用得上，还是记录一下吧"></a>可以本地模拟数据，虽然实际不怎么用得上，还是记录一下吧</h3><p>1、在项目目录里创建一个data.json文件。<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"test"</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="attr">"title"</span>: <span class="string">"模拟数据"</span>, <span class="attr">"text"</span>: <span class="string">"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aspernatur enim, excepturi itaque iure perspiciatis provident sequi suscipit tempora tempore totam? Aspernatur cumque distinctio ea itaque nisi ratione tenetur. Accusantium, repudiandae."</span> &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2、在build目录下的webpack.dev.conf.js添加<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> express = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">'express'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> app = express()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> appData = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">'../data.json'</span>)  <span class="comment">/* 引入根目录下data.json数据文件 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> apiRoutes = express.Router()  <span class="comment">/* 定义express.Router() 对象 */</span></span><br><span class="line">app.use(<span class="string">'/api'</span>, apiRoutes)  <span class="comment">/* 定义接口在/api目录下，方便管理 */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>3、在webpack.dev.conf.js,找到devWebpackConfig的devServer添加<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">before(app) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  app.get(<span class="string">'/api/test'</span>, (req, res) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    res.json(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      code: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      data: appData.test</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>配置重新运行一次，然后在浏览器上本地localhost + 接口显示到数据就可以了,如 <a href="http://localhost:8081/api/test，图待续" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:8081/api/test，图待续</a></p><p>就酱紫，随笔，待续……</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;简单记录一下vue-cli构建项目，真的简单记录。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;安装&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#安装&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;安装&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;安装&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight c&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 全局安装 vue-cli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ npm install --global vue-cli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 创建一个基于 webpack 模板的新项目&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ vue init webpack my-project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 安装依赖，走你&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ cd my-project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ npm run dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
